HWM is a monthly consumer technology publication covering the 3Cs of tech -- Computers, Consumer Electronics & Communications, and now Software and Games.  HWM is known for its authoritative product comparison shootouts, analytical feature stories, benchmarked product reviews and technical walkthroughs.  Feast your eyes on easy-to-read layouts, useful tips and decisive reviews, before plonking that hard-earned dollar on the best technology for you, your social circle and your home.
